or high school and woodrow and wilson high school at the age of  warren tried his hand at the stock exchange buying on his father’s borrowed money some shares of cities service  dollars a piece warren earned the initial  thousand dollar capital by implementing a successful business idea  pinball machines in the hairdresser’s in  buffett bought a controlling stake in producing textile company berkshire hathaway which became his main investment company for years to come in  buffett bought a «national indemnity co» then geico he paid   million and   million for them buffett studied under benjamin graham at columbia university new york according to buffett graham taught him how to make reasonable investments on december   bill gates joined the board of berkshire hathaway as an independent director berkshire hathaway is a conglomerate which includes geico auto insurance benjamin moore paint fruit of the loom textiles and many others thus this is a businessman who has a very developed intuition how to invest money ads tweet share destination on google buzz by mascaliuc victoria others the best businessmen in the world  maps of warren edward buffett map united states  maps nebraska  map omaha others from the best businessmen in the world what do bill gates oprah winfrey warren edward buffett have in common they are neither well known pop stars nor actors but they are still very influential in the world they influence the progress and even the fashion they are the richest and the most influential businessmen they are highly appreciated in the world and they are highly gossiped about their financial condition this poll offers a number of the richest businessmen in the world images of warren edward buffett icons photos figures visions appearances illustrations snapshots captures canvas and pictures of warren edward buffett  the best businessmen in the world warren edward buffett  a prosperous man warren edward buffett  the most famous investor ads video warren edward buffett 