 be greedy only when others are fearful warren buffett fear greedy only i bought a company in the mids called dexter shoe and paid  million for it and it went to zero and i gave about  million worth of berkshire stock which is probably now worth  billion but ive made lots of dumb decisions thats part of the game warren buffett decisions game shoe basically when you get to my age youll really measure your success in life by how many of the people you want to have love you actually do love you warren buffett life love success only buy something that youd be perfectly happy to hold if the market shut down for  years warren buffett happy you down you only have to do a very few things right in your life so long as you dont do too many things wrong warren buffett life long you today people who hold cash equivalents feel comfortable they shouldnt they have opted for a terrible longterm asset one that pays virtually nothing and is certain to depreciate in value warren buffett today value people a publicopinion poll is no substitute for thought warren buffett thought poll substitute if past history was all there was to the game the richest people would be librarians warren buffett history past game should you find yourself in a chronically leaking boat energy devoted to changing vessels is likely to be more productive than energy devoted to patching leaks warren buffett boat yourself energy i sent one email in my life i sent it to jeff raikes at microsoft and it ended up in court in minneapolis so i am one for one warren buffett life i am my life i think the most important factor in getting out of the recession actually is just the regenerative capacity of  of american capitalism warren buffett american important think share this page cite this page citation find on amazon warren buffett related authors steve jobs henry ford bill gates jim rohn stephen covey peter drucker les brown john d rockefeller brainyquote desktop brainyquote mobile site home authors topics quote of th